  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your grill to medium-high heat, around 400°F (200°C).",
    "Season the mackerel fillets with salt, black pepper, smoked paprika, and garlic powder.",
    "Brush the grill grates with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Place the mackerel fillets on the grill and cook for 4 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Transfer the mackerel to a plate and brush with lemon juice.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro and serve hot, with harissa on the side if desired.",
    "Let the mackerel rest for a few minutes before serving.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
